{"Title":"蛋黄奶羹的做法","Primary":["牛奶200毫升","鸡蛋黄4个"],"Auxiliary":["粗砂糖15克"],"Flavoring":[],"Setups":["1.用奶锅直接称量15克粗砂糖","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/112/158/2414612/n2414612_142260302832282.jpg","2.从冰箱取出其他食材","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/112/158/2414612/n2414612_142260303058791.jpg","3.将牛奶倒进锅里，大火煮沸腾","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/112/158/2414612/n2414612_142260303294826.jpg","4.沸腾后转为小火，将蛋黄倒入，并搅拌","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/112/158/2414612/n2414612_142260303472390.jpg","5.将奶羹倒回装蛋黄的容器里，融化掉没倒出来的蛋黄","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/112/158/2414612/n2414612_142260303609321.jpg","6.重新倒进奶锅里煮沸腾即可","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/112/158/2414612/n2414612_142260303903192.jpg","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/112/158/2414612/n2414612_142260303417644.jpg","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/112/158/2414612/n2414612_142260303804847.jpg","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/112/158/2414612/n2414612_142260304037783.jpg","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/112/158/2414612/n2414612_142260304489889.jpg","烹饪技巧","蛋黄奶羹比较稠，如果怕这种口感，可以适量加入少许清水。"]}